  "title": "Submarine Electronics Engineer / Senior Engineer at Changi Naval Base, Up to $4800 (Shuttle service provided)",
  "description": "<p><strong>- 2 years contract (convertible/ renewable)</strong></p><p><strong>- Up to $4800</strong></p><p><strong>- Monday to Friday: 8am to 5:30pm (Shuttle service provided)</strong></p><p><strong>- Changi Naval Base</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Perform maintenance tasks on shipboard electronics systems</li><li>Perform installation/removal work for equipment/systems</li><li>Perform repair and servicing of electronics unit/assemblies</li><li>Management of maintenance operations at team, workshop or department level</li><li>Opportunities for selection to participate in short term overseas attachment and training courses.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Period:</strong></p><ul><li>2 years contract (convertible/ renewable)</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Working Hours:</strong></p><ul><li>Monday to Friday: 8am to 5:30pm</li><li>Shuttle service to and from Tuas Naval Base at Joo Koon (AM) and Joo Koon (PM) MRT | Shuttle service to and from Changi Naval Base at Simei (AM) and Tanah Merah (PM) MRT</li></ul><p><strong>Salary:</strong></p><ul><li>Up to $4800</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Location:</strong></p><ul><li>Changi Naval Base</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma in Electronics Engineering/Telecommunication Engineering/ Digital and Network Engineering/ Mechatronics Engineering</li><li>Other certifications with Electronics related modules may also apply</li><li>Ex-RSN personnel with experience in electronics systems may also apply</li><li>Working knowledge and experience on shipboard electronics systems</li><li>Singaporean only</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Interested applicants, kindly email your detailed resume (<strong>MS Word</strong> format is preferred):</p><p><strong>zikry@successhrc.com.sg </strong>(Reg No: <strong>R2198989</strong>)</p><p><br /></p><p>Please ensure that applications sent through email are <strong>no bigger than 1Mb</strong>.</p><p>We thank all applicants for your interest but regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates would be notified.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Success Resource Centre Pte Ltd</strong> (EA License Number: <strong>04C3201</strong>)</p><p>160 Robinson Road, #13-07/08/09 SBF Center, Singapore 068914</p><p>T: 6337 3183 | W: <a href=\"http://www.successhrc.com.sg/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">www.successhrc.com.sg</a></p>",
